high_descs: Turn right and walk to the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper from the garbage to the right of the toilet.
Back up a bit and face the right side of the toilet.
Place the toilet paper on the left edge of the toilet.
Walk back to the garbage can.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper.
Walk back to the right side of the toilet.
Place the empty roll to the left of the full one.
anns.task_desc: Place two rolls of toilet paper on top of a toilet.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the small red bin to the right of the toilet.
Pick up the toilet paper roll that is in the red bin.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the counter, turn left again to face the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on top of the toilet tank.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and take a step forward, then turn right to face the red bin.
Pick up the toilet paper tube out of the red bin.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the counter, turn left again to face the toilet.
Put the toilet paper tube on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper rolls to the toilet tank.
